@startuml sd_DataInitializer_run
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title DataInitializer.run(args) - 系统启动数据初始化

actor "Spring Boot" as SB
participant "DataInitializer" as Init
participant "UserRepository" as UsrRepo
participant "DepartmentRepository" as DeptRepo
participant "EmployeeRepository" as EmpRepo
participant "SalaryItemRepository" as ItemRepo
participant "SocialSecurityConfig\nRepository" as SsRepo
participant "TaxConfigRepository" as TaxRepo
participant "PasswordEncoder" as Encoder

SB -> Init: run(args)
note right of Init : CommandLineRunner接口\n应用启动后自动执行
Init -> UsrRepo: count()
UsrRepo --> Init: 0 (首次启动)
alt 数据库已初始化(count>0)
  Init --> SB: 跳过初始化
else 首次启动
  note right of Init #F0F8FF
    **Step 1: 初始化用户(4个)**
    admin/finance/hr/employee
    密码BCrypt加密
  end note
  Init -> Encoder: encode("admin123")
  Encoder --> Init: $2a$10$...
  Init -> UsrRepo: save(adminUser + 3 other)
  note right of Init #F0F8FF
    **Step 2: 初始化部门(5个)**
    技术部→前端组+后端组
    销售部/财务部/人事部
  end note
  Init -> DeptRepo: saveAll(departments)
  note right of Init #F0F8FF
    **Step 3: 初始化员工(4人)**
    张三/李四(技术部-北京)
    王五(销售部-上海)
    赵六(财务部-北京)
  end note
  Init -> EmpRepo: saveAll(employees)
  note right of Init #F0F8FF
    **Step 4: 初始化工资项目(14个)**
    基本工资/年功/效益/岗位/补贴...
    含公式项目: 应发合计/个税/实发合计
  end note
  Init -> ItemRepo: saveAll(salaryItems)
  note right of Init #F0F8FF
    **Step 5: 初始化社保费率**
    北京+上海 6险种
    个人+单位比例
  end note
  Init -> SsRepo: saveAll(configs)
  note right of Init #F0F8FF
    **Step 6: 初始化个税税率**
    7级累进: 3%~45%
    含速算扣除数
  end note
  Init -> TaxRepo: saveAll(taxConfigs)
end
Init --> SB: 初始化完成
@enduml
